<br>
If you are indeed in VoLS, perhaps talking to your Guild Leader about the RTA, Rotations and Calendars should have come first. <br>
<br>
If you aren't in VoLS but are in any other Rotational or Calendar entity, you might talk to your Guild Leader first.<br>
<br>
If you aren't in a Rotational or Calendar entity but truly wish to know about the RTA, perhaps reading posts in the 20 pages of posts in the General Forum, the 20 pages of posts in the Flame Forum, the (not sure of the number) pages in the Guild Rep Forum and all the post in the pages of the other &quot;pertinent to the Rotations and Calendars&quot; forums.<br>
